{"tid":1475531,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[求大家聽我講少少野］入黎討論下往後對策 可以嘅話想拎個共識","createTime":"2019-08-15T13:40:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T09:37:05.000Z","uid":167326,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ffb8ae3c88da8ffd7f3ba29cf5dc13dfd74dee6b","tid":1475531,"uid":167326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T13:40:28.000Z","msg":"依架大陸開始屈鳩我地<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">恐怖主義</span></span><br />\n<br />\n以前都可以無視大陸由佢自high打飛機<br />\n但恐怖主義呢招好毒辣<br />\n極有可能<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">影響</span></span>外國對香港支援手段 甚至沉默<br />\n<br />\n就好似新疆西藏咁 利用呢招去鎮壓 <br />\n當控制唔到嘅時候 就比錢搵條友血洗火車站 <br />\n然後<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">矛頭會指向示威者</span></span><br />\n <br />\n前線依架卧底/鬼太多 假如我哋繼續武力升級 會中更多嘅伏。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以我地要 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">集中用經濟戰略</span></span>"},{"pid":"bcbb341690a26d6cc92a5b30d7f44a9d0162cf74","tid":1475531,"uid":167326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T13:40:36.000Z","msg":"我讀政政，入嚟教大家點樣提升政治運動成效<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1470899\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1470899</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上面個po已經講得好清楚以經濟角度攻擊<br />\n效果比直接衝擊大好多 <br />\n<br />\n前線勇武派 連日黎已經付出左好多 <br />\n再被捕落去唔係辦法  <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">遊行/不合作運動照舊 <br />\n但唔好抗衡/衝擊警方防線</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">因為要班狗繼續射催淚彈<br />\n要外國繼續對香港發放有旅遊警示</span></span><br />\n影響旅遊/商業來往 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我相信勇武可以係呢段小時間內休息一下<br />\n嘗試/實驗用經濟角度 對抗政府 重整旗鼓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位手足點睇？"},{"pid":"087f0e2077fc5d61c76c0ebed46693d050354824","tid":1475531,"uid":167326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T13:45:26.000Z","msg":"造好經濟方法<br />\n<br />\n1. 銀行盡量禁現金/換美金保值 <br />\n美金保值 就算輸都係7.7同7.8嘅分別 但港幣失守就仆街了<br />\n<br />\n2. &lsquo;振興&rsquo;旅遊業 <br />\n對外國宣揚香港依架係幾咁刺激 免費體驗催淚毒氣 子彈橫飛<br />\n<br />\n3.機場要再諗諗計 而家唔俾入去睇3D電影 唔知點算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3f02a0d589dd3fd430e52e7e0015b92943864dc","tid":1475531,"uid":167326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T13:48:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e068828165a6e91b230d59c576e46b9546074fbe","tid":1475531,"uid":167326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T13:49:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"866809168b0a1e4ee7419382c55bd0289b128d9e","tid":1475531,"uid":167326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T13:49:38.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"13668a8ed5ce0cfc32964837444bb763c6cc6af7","tid":1475531,"uid":167326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T13:49:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c6f1cfc06c93b31fea1d4d554fe8c5379abb405","tid":1475531,"uid":167326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T13:50:08.000Z","msg":"唉"},{"pid":"fa96c40047bf7f16390d90fd2ecc3a53b63913fa","tid":1475531,"uid":167326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T13:51:52.000Z","msg":"有人會講 why not both.. <br />\n但both嘅同時 有可能突出唔到經濟戰略嘅效果"},{"pid":"56c276024dda39892ab66225a84abf06f33cae4f","tid":1475531,"uid":167326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:09:10.000Z","msg":"冇人想傾下咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"dc899ffe8d6e558c1e0c617f46a8323ba4a6afa6","tid":1475531,"uid":184379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:25:28.000Z","msg":"勇武派都衝左成兩個月<br />\n休息下先，和理非要出來撐下喇"},{"pid":"cd80586aa9c86d48ee15ec612149113f67a72610","tid":1475531,"uid":167326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc899ffe8d6e558c1e0c61